quotes: Success comes with the number of steps towards the right direction.
Become the person who you always dreamed to be.
It's not that complicated. Just do the right things and don't give up.
It's a long process and that's what makes it even more pleasant.
Go. Do the hard stuff. Be proud and rest later.
Rest feels better when you worked hard and was productive before.
Do you want to be the one who pursues and achieves things or the one who complains he couldn't?
The difficult choices are the one that make us strong, resistant and unwavering.
